descriptionHtml:
Bored of your character and want to try something different? I used some glitches to get my orc on lvl 19, around 6 quets done at all, almost nothing. Member of companions...and well, I used money cheat so I could use trainers, but nothing else. You can also choose 6 unused perks :)
As Orc, he\'s very good in smithing, two handed weapons, heavy armor and blocking.


I use this savegame with no NPC greetings mod
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=746

And character face is made by Grffnhwk, its orc from his A Character to be Proud Of pack.
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=427
